    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$4,500 - Calling all project lovers and DIY enthusiasts! This vehicle is definitely a 'diamond in the rough' and is ready for someone with a vision to bring it back to life. It has seen a lot of miles and will need some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, but it\u2019s a fantastic, budget-friendly opportunity for a mechanic or hobbyist looking for their next big challenge!",
