      "description": "We are privileged to present this exceptional vehicle, currently held in impeccable condition. This unit has been maintained to an exacting standard, presenting in a state that mirrors its original delivery. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a history of meticulous stewardship, offering an unparalleled driving experience for the most discerning collector. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
